{"tid":1458630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[邊個話塞地鐵就係鬼] 去機場 去機場 去機場！","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:45:40.000Z","uid":241239,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dc660df8304f57e104003253c9eda10378a5f56e","tid":1458630,"uid":241239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"宜家呢個時候話塞地鐵嘅絕對係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先，搞地鐵容易引發民怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二，會分散去機場嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你話朝頭早搞完地鐵之後再去機場都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機場一早開始就要人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣唔小心搞到去機場嘅巴絲更唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，大部份港豬香港人都唔介意你機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為唔影響佢哋返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家我哋唔可以再流失淺黃淺藍支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家記得 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去機場</span>"},{"pid":"0c5bfa9d8ec3dabaac759a72a79d4f770ef43a9e","tid":1458630,"uid":241239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272fd818ca05d2c10a8d910f4b2db760740522d0","tid":1458630,"uid":303520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df55c82ac2986735861ccfd411d5ab5ab6d2be3a","tid":1458630,"uid":292569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07d074e77acf5fdcbc6df729073e41caf3e7f2a1","tid":1458630,"uid":241239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"42161ad5ecb2f0257e71d1657d7193a594e72bdb","tid":1458630,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"去機場la"},{"pid":"31b83868dd516c12a686ed51da53a390536a2e77","tid":1458630,"uid":128883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">塞機場好過塞鐵<br />\n成效和對政府壓力更大<br />\n<br />\n最低收入的一群真的手停口停，佢哋真係唔返工唔得，你咁搞你叫佢哋點支持/同意你？<br />\n<br />\n普羅民意 很重要， 我哋嘅敵人唔係普羅大眾 而係政府， 點解要 減少自己嘅支持者而增加自己嘅敵人呢？<br />\n<br />\n除非你係鬼啦！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"640b489e7104ca18721ffa119d1d82fe43619e52","tid":1458630,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:56.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得太多post太亂？我整左個策略、行動、文宣方向精華集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7AT6Db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7AT6Db.png&h=b6163964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場檢討POST懶人包</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1</a><br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1</a><br />\n有消息嘗試用舉牌方式同人講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1</a><br />\n我覺得今日散水無錯，互屌先係真中計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1</a><br />\n[賽後檢討] 今日機場有無散水既都麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1</a><br />\n下次搞再機場唔該幫下啲旅客<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1</a><br />\n今日機場事件有少少諗法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1</a><br />\n我係散水撚，我係嚟道歉嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好需要你幫手報料/update/宣傳呀"},{"pid":"8f19d281e03b9d8b5643dc8632ed8ce772145f2d","tid":1458630,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458192/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458192/page/1</a><br />\n見到有人想一連四日塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要一言堂 咁不如問下大家意見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n塞鐵公投（結果：反對為主）"},{"pid":"71f22552f50f2fc136a88449e1014d8f7bae6512","tid":1458630,"uid":241239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31b83868dd516c12a686ed51da53a390536a2e77","tid":1458630,"uid":128883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">塞機場好過塞鐵<br />\n成效和對政府壓力更大<br />\n<br />\n最低收入的一群真的手停口停，佢哋真係唔返工唔得，你咁搞你叫佢哋點支持/同意你？<br />\n<br />\n普羅民意 很重要， 我哋嘅敵人唔係普羅大眾 而係政府， 點解要 減少自己嘅支持者而增加自己嘅敵人呢？<br />\n<br />\n除非你係鬼啦！</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637cf1f6f070abcfc6bf7da67e320f8e369fd98a","tid":1458630,"uid":241239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"5d3aa0167c5517cb17abcc3c2eeb44aa98239d75","tid":1458630,"uid":241239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff525f9018e86d666427896e8b907a3aebcef83c","tid":1458630,"uid":40131,"like